Package org.apache.calcite.adapter.geode.rel

Query provider based on Apache Geode (Gemfire) In Memory Data Grid

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GeodeRel
    Relational expression that uses Geode calling convention.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeodeAggregate
    Implementation of Aggregate relational expression in Geode.
    GeodeEnumerator
    Enumerator that reads from a Geode Regions.
    GeodeFilter
    Implementation of Filter relational expression in Geode.
    GeodeFilter.Translator
    Translates RexNode expressions into Geode expression strings.
    GeodeProject
    Implementation of Project relational expression in Geode.
    GeodeRel.GeodeImplementContext
    Shared context used by the GeodeRel relations.
    GeodeRules
    Rules and relational operators for GeodeRel.CONVENTION calling convention.
    GeodeRules.GeodeAggregateRule
    Rule to convert Aggregate to a GeodeAggregate.
    GeodeRules.GeodeConverterRule
    Base class for planner rules that convert a relational expression to Geode calling convention.
    GeodeRules.GeodeFilterRule
    Rule to convert a LogicalFilter to a GeodeFilter.
    GeodeRules.GeodeProjectRule
    Rule to convert a LogicalProject to a GeodeProject.
    GeodeRules.GeodeSortLimitRule
    Rule to convert the Limit in Sort to a GeodeSort.
    GeodeRules.RexToGeodeTranslator
    Translator from RexNode to strings in Geode's expression language.
    GeodeSchema
    Schema mapped onto a Geode Region.
    GeodeSchemaFactory
    Factory that creates a GeodeSchema.
    GeodeSort
    Implementation of Sort relational expression in Geode.
    GeodeTable
    Table based on a Geode Region
    GeodeTable.GeodeQueryable<T>
    Implementation of Queryable based on a GeodeTable.
    GeodeTableScan
    Relational expression representing a scan of a Geode collection.
    GeodeToEnumerableConverter
    Relational expression representing a scan of a table in a Geode data source.
    GeodeToEnumerableConverterRule
    Rule to convert a relational expression from GeodeRel.CONVENTION to EnumerableConvention.
